---
// Acknowledgement of Country — Whadjuk Noongar (Perth)
---
<section class="bg-cream border-t border-forest/10" aria-label="Acknowledgement of Country">
  <div class="container-page section-tight">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center reveal">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-4" aria-hidden="true">
        <!-- Aboriginal flag -->
        <svg width="34" height="22" viewBox="0 0 60 40" class="rounded-sm shadow-sm">
          <rect width="60" height="20" fill="#000" /><rect y="20" width="60" height="20" fill="#C8102E" />
          <circle cx="30" cy="20" r="8" fill="#FFB81C" />
        </svg>
        <!-- Torres Strait Islander flag -->
        <svg width="34" height="22" viewBox="0 0 60 40" class="rounded-sm shadow-sm">
          <rect width="60" height="40" fill="#2E5E9E" />
          <rect width="60" height="3" y="4" fill="#000" /><rect width="60" height="3" y="33" fill="#000" />
          <rect width="60" height="2.5" y="7" fill="#0B7A3B" /><rect width="60" height="2.5" y="30.5" fill="#0B7A3B" />
          <path d="M30 14l1.6 4.8H37l-4.3 3 1.6 4.8L30 23.6 25.7 26.6l1.6-4.8-4.3-3h5.4z" fill="#fff" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <p class="eyebrow text-forest mb-3">Acknowledgement of Country</p>
      <p class="text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
        PhysioLogix acknowledges the Whadjuk people of the Noongar Nation as the
        Traditional Custodians of the land on which we work and treat. We pay our
        respects to Elders past and present, and extend that respect to all Aboriginal
        and Torres Strait Islander peoples. We welcome Aboriginal and Torres Strait
        Islander patients to our clinic.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
